data.description: Located in the established community of Belmont Park is a gorgeous two level 3 bedrooms/2.5 bath home.  A conservative arch entry leads to a huge family room and kitchen.  The utility room includes a walk-in pantry with shelves.  Wood spindle railing escorts you to a huge game room, primary bedroom with a full bath to include a separate shower and jetted garden tub.  All bedrooms including the game room having ceiling fans.  The home is located less than 5 minutes from I35 for easy access to major shopping and entertainment in San Antonio, New Braunfels, San Marcos and Austin.
